degree: Vocational High School - Computer and Network Engineering
desc: Entered Vocational School majoring in Computer and Network Engineering. Learned about programming, computers and networks for 3 years and gained experience by participating in Students Skills Competition (LKS) in 2015 and 2016 from District / City, Provincial to National Levels.

Continuing study at the Faculty of Engineering, majoring in INFORMATICS ENGINEERING. Deepen and fullfill knowledge that has been learned since High School especially programming and software development.
